We recommended that the Local Chief Executive (LCE):

(51) Direct the Municipal Accountant to strictly comply with the timelines prescribed under COA Circular No. 2019-001 on the submission of barangay financial transaction documents to the Auditor, which is within ten working days from receipt of the transmittal letter of the PB; 

(52) Look into the possibility of augmenting the personnel of the Municipal Accountant’s Office with personnel from other departments, especially during report preparation and/or allowing them to render overtime services, subject to availability of funds, to ensure the submission of the accounts and financial reports within the mandated deadlines.

We recommended that Management:

