Direct the OIC-Municipal Accountant to immediately submit the unsubmitted CY 2016 Monthly Trial Balances and Quarterly/Year-End FS and henceforth, to prepare and submit the Monthly Trial Balance and Quarterly Financial Statements with complete Schedules and Annexes within the prescribed timeframe in accordance with the abovementioned existing rules and regulations; 
